    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 33. 26 – 29, Mecometopus martinsi sp. nov., holotype female: 26, dorsal habitus; 27, ventral habitus; 28, lateral habitus; 29, head, frontal view. 30, Recchia volcanensis sp. nov., holotype female, upper eye lobes. 31, Recchia lanei, holotype female, upper eye lobes. 32 – 33, Recchia procera, paratype female: 32, upper eye lobes; 33, elytral apices." ;
